<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC5FFA0625EFE45C6B5FE28" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[793,1006,402,429]" pageId="9" pageNumber="310" pagination="282 - 286" refId="ref10062" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1995 c) Record of three species of Rhombognathus (Halacaridae: Acari) from Indian Ocean region. Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 92, 282 - 286." type="journal article" year="1995">Chatterjee (1995c)</bibRefCitation>
